Pistorius is an organist at a church in the town of Sinclair's boarding school. Sinclair stalks him, secretly listening to him play music. They eventually meet when Sinclair follows him to a bar. He teaches Sinclair a lot about Abraxas. Pistorius is a foil for Demianâ€”he is Sinclair's mentor during a period of time when Demian is absent from his life.